info.name: The Devil Wears Prada tumblr logo replacement
info.description: A "The Devil Wears Prada" triangle which replaces the "tumblr." logo at the top of your tumblr dashboard

style.css: @namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml); @-moz-document url-prefix('http://www.tumblr.com/'), url-prefix('https://www.tumblr.com/')   { #logo {height: 0 !important; width: 0 !important; padding-left: 350px !important; padding-top: 44px !important; background: url(http://25.media.tumblr.com/7565ee2bbbc76d593a9f4d6e12207443/tumblr_met0g5jQPi1rgncooo1_250.png) no-repeat !important;}}
